'''育碧美因茨'''（{{lang-de|Ubisoft Mainz}}，前称'''Related Designs'''）是一家位于[[德国|德国]][[美因茨|美因茨]]的游戏开发工作室，专门从事PC平台的战略游戏。2007年，育碧收购该公司30％的股权。<ref name="UbiBuys30%">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13483|title=Ubisoft Acquires SunFlowers, Anno Franchise|last=Boyer|first=Brandon|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|date=2007-04-11|accessdate=2013-04-12|archive-date=2013-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130512135742/http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=13483|dead-url=no}}</ref>2013年4月，育碧购买购买该公司剩余70％的股权，使该公司成为育碧的全资子公司。<ref name="UbiBuysRest">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/news/ubisoft-completes-anno-dev-acquisition-6406894|title=Ubisoft completes Anno dev acquisition|last=Makuch|first=Eddie|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|date=2013-04-12|accessdate=2013-04-12|archive-date=2013-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130415002104/http://www.gamespot.com/news/ubisoft-completes-anno-dev-acquisition-6406894|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年6月，该公司完全融入[[Ubisoft_Blue_Byte|Ubisoft Blue Byte]]。<ref>[http://www.gamezone.de/Ubisoft-Firma-15823/News/Ubisoft-Ehemaliges-Related-Designs-Studio-ab-sofort-unter-Blue-Byte-Flagge-1125838/ ''Gamezone article''] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamezone.de/Ubisoft-Firma-15823/News/Ubisoft-Ehemaliges-Related-Designs-Studio-ab-sofort-unter-Blue-Byte-Flagge-1125838/ |date=20180612232543 }} vom 18. Juni 2014</ref>Blue Byte后于2019年8月内部重组，工作室更为现名。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-08-20-ubisoft-rebrands-its-german-studios |title=Ubisoft rebrands its German studios |first=Rebekah |last=Valentine |date=2019-08-20 |website={{le|GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz}} |access-date=2019-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130204124/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-08-20-ubisoft-rebrands-its-german-studios |archive-date=2019-11-30 |url-status=live }}</ref>

